    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a knob of <strong>butter</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced mushrooms </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 7-8 min or until browned</p><p>Once browned, transfer the <strong>cooked mushrooms</strong> to a plate (reserve the pan!)</p>",
