    {
      "instruction": "<p>Mix your <strong>honey</strong> and <strong>truffle oil</strong> in a bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>– this is your <strong>truffled honey</strong></p><p>Chop your<strong> tomatoes </strong>roughly</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with<strong> </strong>kitchen paper</p><p>Set the<strong> washed salad</strong> and <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong> aside until serving</p>",
