    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the <strong>ciabatta halves</strong> are lightly toasted, spoon the <strong>rarebit sauce</strong> all over them</p><p>Tip: Make sure to spread the sauce to the edges of the ciabatta to stop the corners burning!</p><p>Add the <strong>cooked mushrooms</strong> to the baking tray</p><p>Return the tray to the grill and cook for 3-4 min or until the rarebit sauce is lightly browned – these are your <strong>rarebit toasts</strong></p>",
